{"tid":2364916,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美資管理人道富跪低 盈富基金恢復投資被美制裁股份","createTime":"2021-01-13T10:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T14:01:53.000Z","uid":164771,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"10c22e669012aee4fe08592a10bd693e8049310c","tid":2364916,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:47:10.000Z","msg":"特朗普禁止美國企業或個人投資解放軍關連企業，引發由美資道富管理的盈富基金（2800）早前宣布停向中移動（941）、聯通（762）及中海油（883）進行新投資，市場更有建議撤換經理人。不過，道富最新發出通知，指作為盈富基金之經理人，將於明日（1月14日）起將恢復對屬於恒指成份股公司的受制裁實體進行投資。<br />\n<br />\n道富指，自美國於1月6日發佈更新的制裁名單以來，作爲盈富基金之基金經理一直努力檢閱若干事項，以繼續投資於所有恒生指數成份股。道富將如招股書所述，繼續努力實現盈富基金的投資目標，提供緊貼恒生指數表現的投資回報。<br />\n<br />\n道富又指，鑑於盈富基金對香港市場的重要性，理解此事關乎重大公衆利益，並希望恢復投資一舉能證明我們如過去21年般，始終致力恪守盈富基金緊貼恒生指數表現的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210113/O5YYKKLOCJAEHLGCCFC3CIWOFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210113%2FO5YYKKLOCJAEHLGCCFC3CIWOFE%2F&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvERT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=551f2d9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210113%2FO5YYKKLOCJAEHLGCCFC3CIWOFE%2F&h=46571bb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210113/O5YYKKLOCJAEHLGCCFC3CIWOFE/</a>"},{"pid":"84f90e9102f0ef6e4d94a893e71a9412e86eb647","tid":2364916,"uid":163529,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:50:51.000Z","msg":"MPF 無了！一鋪清袋"},{"pid":"1cf841b02cddc384c1d81f25d46116cc39b15817","tid":2364916,"uid":74361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:51:09.000Z","msg":"廢燈都唔制裁嫁啦"},{"pid":"4cbc212e0f78ce2f04e249c7fb8a8315740951a8","tid":2364916,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:54:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr